'''''A Dry White Season''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1989 iyobowe na Euzhan Palcy ikinwamo na Donald Sutherland<ref>A Dry White Season (1989) | The Criterion Collection <nowiki>https://www.criterion.com</nowiki> › films › 29148-a-dry-white-...</ref>, Jürgen Prochnow, Marlon Brando, Janet Suzman, Zakes Mokae naSusan Sarandon Yanditswe na Colin Welland na Palcy<ref>'A Dry White Season' - The Washington Post <nowiki>https://www.washingtonpost.com</nowiki> › movies › videos › a...</ref>, ishingiye ku gitabo cya André Brink cyitwa '''''A Dry White Season'''''<ref>A Dry White Season - Toronto International Film Festival <nowiki>https://www.tiff.net</nowiki> › events › a-dry-white-season</ref>. Robert Bolt nawe yatanze umusanzu wo gusubiramo amashusho atemewe<ref>30 years after making history with 'A Dry White Season,' director <nowiki>https://www.latimes.com</nowiki> › entertainment › movies › la-...</ref>. Yashyizwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] mumwaka wa 1976 kandi ivuga kubyerekeye ivanguramoko . Brando yatorewe muri Oscar<ref>30 years after making history with 'A Dry White Season,' director <nowiki>https://www.latimes.com</nowiki> › entertainment › movies › la-...</ref> nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza.

== Umugambi ==
Mu 1976, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] mu gihe cya apartheid, Ben Du Toit ( Donald Sutherland ) ni umwarimu w’ishuri ryo muri [[Afurika]] yepfo ku ishuri ry’abazungu gusa. Umunsi umwe<ref>Euzhan Palcy Remembers the Fight to Make A Dry White ... <nowiki>https://www.vulture.com</nowiki> › 2020/06 › euzhan-palcy-reme...</ref>, umuhungu w’umurimyi we, Gordon Ngubene ( Winston Ntshona ), yakubiswe n’abapolisi bera nyuma yo gufatwa n’abapolisi mu myigaragambyo y’amahoro hagamijwe politiki nziza y’uburezi ku birabura muri [[Afurika]] yepfo<ref>Critic Reviews for A Dry White Season - Metacritic <nowiki>https://www.metacritic.com</nowiki> › movie › critic-reviews</ref>. Gordon asaba Ben ubufasha. Ben amaze kwanga gutabara kubera ko yizeraga abapolisi, Gordon na we yafashwe na polisi kandi akorerwa iyicarubozo na Kapiteni Stolz ( Jürgen Prochnow ). Bitandukanye n'ubushake bw'umugore we Susan ( Janet Suzman ) n'umukobwa we Suzette ( Susannah Harker )<ref>A Dry White Season - French Film Festival <nowiki>http://frenchfilmfestival.us</nowiki> › portfolio › a-dry-season</ref>, Ben agerageza kumenya byinshi ku ibura ry'umurimyi we wenyine. Nyuma y’ivumburwa ry’ubwicanyi bwakozwe na Gordon n’umuhungu we bombi<ref>A Dry White Season (1989) | Radio Times <nowiki>https://www.radiotimes.com</nowiki> › movie-guide › a-dry-whi...</ref>, Ben yahisemo kugeza iki kibazo imbere y’urukiko na Ian McKenzie ( Marlon Brando ) nk'umunyamategeko ariko aratsindwa. Nyuma yaho<ref>A Dry White Season | Riverside Studios <nowiki>https://riversidestudios.co.uk</nowiki> › see-and-do › a-dry-whit...</ref>, akomeje gukora wenyine kandi ashyigikira itsinda rito ryabirabura, barimo umushoferi we Stanley Makhaya ( Zakes Mokae ), kugira ngo afashe abandi bateze imbere imibereho<ref>A Dry White Season | novel by Brink | Britannica <nowiki>https://www.britannica.com</nowiki> › topic › A-Dry-White-Seas...</ref>.

